                        <h1 class="post-title text-center" id="page">Hangar Çadırı</h1>
                        <figure class="mb-25"><img class="w-100 img-fluid rounded mb-3 shadow-sm" style="max-height: 480px; object-fit: cover;" src="/style/brand/img/depo-cadiri5.webp" alt="Maltepe Büyük çaplı çelik hangar çadırı" loading="lazy" /></figure>
